i have decided to give up...i can't take it anymore...life is the worst that it has been in a very long time...well actually things were worse about a week or two ago...things just get too hard and i can't handle it...i'm no longer with the person that matters most to me and i can't take it. Tim is all that matters...he has always been there for me and told me that everythings going to be ok...he was there for me when i fucked up...BIG TIME! <i have fucked up alot too> i've blamed things on him that he hasn't done and then i make up some lame excuse to justify what i was thinking while fucking up...life is just pointless sometime and right now is one of those times...i can't seem to see through all the shit thats in front of me and it's driving me over the edge. nothing is exciting anymore...nothing is worth anything anymore...this...i just don't know anymore. all i want is to be with the man i love...to be with him and have everyone else just leave me the fuck alone...he's the one i want...if i loose him now...it just might be the end...

so this is my first entry...this should be excting...not really but whatever... so i guess there are several things on my mind...one,with my aunts wedding on Sunday i find myself wondering,what if there is no one out there for me...what if i am ment to be alone...to die alone...i find myself asking what if more often too and thinking about things i would have never drempt of about a year ago. tonight i was downtown with my friends Chels and Banonas. Chels said something that really got to me. "if i were to see myself now from a 13 year old versoin of myself i would hate myself." i feel the same way. about three years ago i was against everything i am now...this is who i am and there is nothing i can do to change that. i mean i never smoked until about a year ago and all i remember is saying, "i can't believe i'm actually smoking..." i feel now that everything i once lived for is now dead and therefor i should be as well...there is so much shit happening right now that sometimes i just can't handle it anymore. what ifs are drinving me mad...
